loat<openparen>x<closeparen><comma><space>3<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>y_rounded<space>=<space>round<openparen>float<openparen>y<closeparen><comma><space>3<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>coords.append<openparen>f<quote>POINT<openparen><opencurly>x_rounded<closecurly><space><opencurly>y_rounded<closecurly><closeparen><quote><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>except<space>ValueError:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>pass<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>i<space>+=<space>1<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>else:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>break<lf><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>linestring<space>=<space>f<quote><opencurly><apos><semicolon><space><apos>.join<openparen>coords<closeparen><closecurly><quote><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>feature.setAttribute<openparen><quote>Coverage.Geometry<quote><comma><space>linestring<closeparen><lf><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.pyoutput<openparen>feature<closeparen><lf><lf><lf>    OUTPUT PYOUTPUT FEATURE_TYPE PythonCaller_OUTPUT
